HEADWORD: Quadrivalve
<hw>Quad"ri*valve</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Quadri-</ets> + <ets>valve</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>quadrivalve</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Dehiscent into
four similar parts; four-valved; <as>as, a <ex>quadrivalve</ex>
pericarp</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
