==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Quadrivalve
<hw>Quad"ri*valve</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Arch.)</fld> <def>A door,
shutter, or the like, having four folds.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Quadrivalvular</ent>⟦br⟧
